citoid-citoiddialog-search-label: URL, DOI, ISBN, PMC/PMID, QID, title, or citation
citoid-citoiddialog-use-general-error-me: Te koŋ baŋ nyɛ yizie ko fo. Fo na baŋ maale la kaŋa ne fo nuuri a yi a "{{int:citoid-citoiddialog-mode-manual}}" tɔ a sazu ŋa.
